    <div class="faq-a" id="how-does-white-label-seo-work"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>You sell SEO packages to your clients at retail rates. You contract with a white-label provider at wholesale rates. The provider executes content creation, local SEO, reporting, or other services. They deliver the work unbranded or through your branded portal. You present the results to your client as your own. The margin between retail and wholesale is your profit.</p></div></div>
