      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="is-white-label-seo-ethical"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. White label SEO is a standard business practice used by advertising agencies, consulting firms, and software resellers worldwide. You maintain the client relationship, set the strategy, and own the results. The provider acts as a fulfillment partner, similar to how a general contractor uses specialized subcontractors. Transparency about your role is a business choice, not an ethical violation.</p></div></div>
  </div>
