      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="does-ai-seo-replace-traditional-seo-specialists"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. AI SEO automates research, drafting, publishing, and reporting. It does not replace strategic thinking, client relationships, or quality judgment. The best agencies use AI to handle repetitive execution while their specialists focus on strategy, client communication, and business development. The role evolves from writer to director.</p></div></div>
